            h1(tabindex=index++) Let's get in touch!

            .conversation.jscritical
                input#message(type='text', placeholder='Send a message to my bot', tabindex=index++)

            ul
                li: a#mail(href='mailto:ijee@tuta.io?subject=Hello%20from%20a%20visitor,%20Greg', tabindex=index++) Send me an email
                li: a#tweet(href='https://twitter.com/0x006A', tabindex=index++) Tweet to me
